## Marking a class as a pipe

 pipes component  typescript  class Component Class  `@Component` Class  Component  pipis class  `@Pipe`  Class  ``( - ) pipes  = 2  = 10  2^10 = 1024

1.  Angular CLI  pipes class

    ```bash
